udent experience and success, cultivate and empower faculty leaders, drive life-changing discoveries and strengthen connections to our communities.  At the same time, each college and unit is chasing its own ambitious vision to create access for and offer an exceptional experience to tomorrow’s leaders in their fields.  All while assembling a faculty of thought leaders and ground breakers who will illuminate young minds while delivering solutions for today’s challenges. Find out what we’re focused on in the areas that are most important to you.      Stories of Impact        Understand Giving  Review giving strategies that will support UIC and meet your philanthropic goals.          Seize an Opportunity  Read about how donors make an impact in the four areas we see as most important.          University of Illinois Foundation  Get to know the official  private-gift-receiving agency for the University of Illinois.           Stories of Impact       Thank you for Supporting IGNITE: The Campaign for UIC    Posted on November 20, 2019        Former Faculty Member Supports Students and Provides for Son    Posted on September 06, 2019             Chancellor Amiridis Celebrates Donors and Advocates for Supporting UIC    Posted on April 11, 2019             UIC CHAMPIONS NETWork    Posted on March 01, 2019             UIC receives $1M bequest from beloved art history professor    Posted on December 11, 2018               Alumnus who overcame challenges helps others do the same    Taylor Kasper  |  Posted on November 14, 2018        $1.5 million from The Davee Foundation boosts UIC scholarship fund    Brian Flood  |  Posted on July 12, 2018             TransUnion and UIC announce endowed professorship of data science    Posted on June 18, 2018             IGNITE Campaign Update    Posted on April 20, 2018             Former Student and Faculty Member Inspired to Give Back    Taylor Kasper  |  Posted on March 19, 2018                 Contact UIC Advancement     Phone: 312-413-8